episodes.title: Episode 25: Twin Flames Universe - Sparks or Scams?
episodes.description: Join us as we talk about a cult with a dark secret. Warning for sensitive content. Dee and Ris discuss the medical and psychiatric perspectives behind this case, based upon their experiences as nurses.
